V0704_01_00_00_0.text:
My deck is good to go!
Let's rock!

V0704_01_00_01_0.text: Let's settle this in a Rush Duel!

V0704_01_00_03_0.text: No one knows who'll win or lose until we actually Duel!

V0704_01_00_04_0.text:
Are you ready?
Because I'm ready!

V0704_01_00_05_0.text: I'm here to boot you off the stage!

V0704_01_00_07_0.text: If you think I'm still a beginner, that's your mistake!

V0704_01_00_08_0.text: Against Gavin, I have to make every move count.

V0704_01_00_09_0.text: Are you really an alien, Celestia?

V0704_01_00_10_0.text:
I know how tough Roa is more than anyone.
But I'm gonna win!

V0704_01_00_11_0.text:
Let's Rush Duel, Mimi!
It'll be... like you say... phat?

V0704_01_00_12_0.text: It's always been my dream to jam with Princess G.

V0704_01_00_12_1.text:
I can't believe it's coming true!
Let's Duel, Princess G!

V0704_03_00_01_0.text: It's the countdown to the finale!

V0704_03_00_03_0.text: I'll knock you out from the very first tune!

V0704_03_00_04_0.text: There's still a lot of Duel left to play!

V0704_03_00_05_0.text: I may be down, but I'm still jamming!

V0704_05_00_00_0.text: My seven strings can still play the meanest riff!

V0704_06_01_00_0.text: I won't let you do that!

V0704_07_09_00_0.text: This is the card I Set!

V0704_07_09_01_0.text: I'll use the card I Set!

V0704_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0704_16_00_00_0.text:
Time for the grand finale!
And there'll be no encore!

V0704_21_00_00_0.text: Not losing my cool is paying off big time!

V0704_21_00_01_0.text: I'm all tuned up for whatever comes next!

V0704_21_00_03_0.text: I have plenty of surprises in store for later.

V0704_28_00_00_0.text: Rush Duels are always a great time!

V0704_28_00_01_0.text: Goes to show I can really perform when I need to.

V0704_28_00_02_0.text: I almost lost, but I didn't give up!

V0704_28_00_03_0.text:
I can do anything in a Rush Duel.
That's what makes it fun!

V0704_28_00_04_0.text: When I'm on the beat, the concert can't be beat!

V0704_28_00_05_0.text: I love both music and Rush Duels!

V0704_28_00_06_0.text: I haven't rocked this hard in forever!

V0704_28_00_07_0.text: This is what happens when you try to force your own game!

V0704_28_00_07_1.text: You're the one who needs to study more - not me!

V0704_28_00_08_0.text: Roa, you usually shine brighter than this...

V0704_28_00_09_0.text: This proves you're not ready to go solo!

V0704_28_00_10_0.text:
You shouldn't party all night.
We all need 8 hours of sleep.

V0704_28_00_11_0.text:
The Duel's over.
You can stop pretending to be an alien.

V0704_28_00_12_0.text:
Ha!
I strike out Duelists like you on the daily!

V0704_28_00_13_0.text:
That's a home run!
I'm winning the triple crown!

V0704_28_00_14_0.text: I won't give up Rush Duels or music because I love 'em both!

V0704_29_00_00_0.text:
No way!
This can't be real!

V0704_29_00_01_0.text:
I knew this would happen...
But I'm not happy about it!

V0704_29_00_02_0.text:
What? I lost?
...Kinda shocked to be honest.

V0704_29_00_03_0.text:
I lost...
But I still enjoyed Rush Dueling you!

V0704_29_00_04_0.text:
I'm so hungry...
That mic stand looks like a churro...

V0704_29_00_05_0.text: I expect nothing less from the creator of Rush Duels.

V0704_29_00_06_0.text:
You can stop smiling now!
I was just off my game today!

V0704_29_00_07_0.text: Your Sogetsu Style is really something.

V0704_29_00_07_1.text: Something I don't understand - but still something.

V0704_29_00_08_0.text: Even I didn't know Roa could rock this hard!

V0704_33_00_01_0.text: I'm gonna play the greatest gig in history!

V0704_33_00_03_0.text: No one can stop me from doing what I want!

V0704_33_00_04_0.text:
I have a new way to play!
Listen!

V0704_33_00_06_0.text: I'm so hungry that I can't think straight...

V0704_33_00_07_0.text: I can't let the crowd hear my tummy growl...

V0704_43_00_01_0.text: This Duel's more important for me than for you!

V0704_30_00_02_0.text: Can you hurry up and make a move?

V0704_34_00_00_0.text: I didn't ask for anyone's help!

V0704_34_00_01_0.text:
I can't tell you!
It's a secret!

V0704_34_00_03_0.text: The fact you're so calm is scaring me...

V0704_34_00_04_0.text: What are you planning to do? Because I have no clue!

V0704_34_00_05_0.text: Only you would fall for that.

V0704_34_00_06_0.text: I wish I had a brother as sweet as you!

V0704_34_00_07_0.text: Have two bowls of Dragias and Prima Guitarna Curry!

V0704_34_00_08_0.text: The Rockin’ Romin's here to solve all your problems!

V0704_34_00_09_0.text: I let my guard down and stepped right into their trap.

V0704_34_00_10_0.text:
The Rockin' Romin's superpower!
Miracle Problem Solver Beam!

V0704_34_00_12_0.text: Your head looks like a bowl of calamari...

V0704_34_00_13_0.text: Ramen Hut's bowls are so yummy... *drool*

V0704_35_00_00_0.text:
I'm Romin Kassidy!
RoaRomin's lead guitar!

V0704_35_00_01_0.text:
I'm Romin Kassidy!
Fifth grader at Goha #7 Elementary!

V0704_36_00_04_0.text: Sorry... But I believe in you!

V0704_36_00_08_0.text:
You're up, Luke.
Don't do anything crazy!

V0704_36_00_10_0.text: Don't let your fans down, Roa!
